<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-59-0434 </DOCNO><TEXT>In two previous papers methods of calculating the cross sections integratedover solid angle for the coherent and incoherent scattering of polarizedX-rays by atoms into an arbitrarily placed circular aperture were presented.The errors associated with the measurement of scattered X-rays for quantitativeanalyses are discussed in the present paper.</TEXT></DOC>